author: COMSOL
description: The topology optimized Tesla microvalve is used as inspiration for a parameterized geometry. The optimization of this geometry takes erosion and dilation of the geometry into account by optimizing over a parametric sweep. In this example the optimization is driven by the worst of the three geometries realized in every parametric sweep.
label: tesla_microvalve_parameter_optimization.mph
